{
  "stem": "17543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was saying to a girl who was a bit older than me, I said, this is the people live around this area.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they don't know we are here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could they let them know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, there was somebody-- because she understood German-- and somebody heard when these German soldiers were talking to one another at work-- you know, where we was working-- they were scared a few people who tried to get out climbing the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the fence at night.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody somehow got out on that window, and they was swimming for a-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they got him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they was boasting to one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I'm going to have another medal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's really frightening, because everybody had most likely-- not just me-- you know, I'd wonder how could we get out, because we were surrounded with people who wasn't that far, and they might not see we are there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't attempt, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would think about it too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I was thinking about it was some clothes-- you know, take off and write in big letters, you know, we are here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also in camp Mathausen, again, was a washroom with no windows in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was all broken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was only cold water in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was awfully difficult to-- to clean ourselves, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was absolutely terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only at work, but I mean, you couldn't undress.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could wash your face, hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not any other area, because these men were coming and going who worked there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and the soldiers-- you couldn't tell how long they would be away.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
